Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
I think it is a good thing. The freshmen just left home to live apart from their parents.  So it is important that they have a feeling of home, and they can make frienda quickly. On campus living is good to make friends and know other students of the university more quickly.